<h3>Hello,</h3>
<p>Thank you for buying locally through KFOM! The following is a summary of your orders for the week. All
orders must be picked up this <strong>Thursday between 5-7 pm in the back room of the Klamath Tool Library</strong>
(1221 Main St.) Remember that you must pay each food producer individually. Please write a <u>separate
check to each individual food producer</u> for the totals listed below and leave in the drop box when you
pick up. If you choose to pay with cash, please separate exact change into envelopes for each producer.
Only producers whose minimum total was met will fulfill orders, which are listed below.</p>
<br />
  <table style='width:100%;'>
    <thead>
      <th>Producer Name</th>
      <th>Contact Info</th>
      <th>Order Details</th>
      <th>Check Payable To</th>
      <th>Total</th>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <% @order_items.each do |seller, items| %>
      <% subtotal = 0 %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= seller.profile.business_name %></td>
        <td>
          <li><%= seller.email %></li>
          <li><%= seller.profile.phone_formatted %></li>
        </td>
        <td>
          <% items.each do |i| %>
            <% subtotal = subtotal.to_f + (i.quantity.to_i * i.post.price.to_f) %>
            <li><%= "#{i.post.title} - Quantity to pick up: #{i.quantity}"  %> </li>
          <% end %>
        </td>
        <td><%= seller.profile.payable_to %></td>
        <td><%= number_to_currency(subtotal) %></td>
      </tr>
      <% end %>
    </tbody>
  </table>
<br />
