and personal responsibility. Please make sure you understand the instructions below:</em>
<br />
<h4>Payment:</h4>
<p>If you would like to pay using your SNAP benefits, please call the Klamath Farmer’s Market to pay over
the phone at 541-273- 1102 from 9 am – 9 pm, Monday – Friday. Please communicate your total
balance and pay any remaining balance directly to the farmer.</p>

<p>Failure to pay will result in cancellation of your membership with KFOM. If you fail to pick up your order
during the specified hours, you will not be able to arrange an alternative pickup time. Please take only
what you ordered and pay the food producers for their hard work.</p>

<p>Your orders will not be aggregated into one bundle, so make sure to pick up each of your orders from
each producer.</p>

<h4>Questions:</h4>

<p>Please contact food producers directly with any questions regarding your order. If you are unable to
contact the producer, please contact KFOM.</p>

